snippet.title: Tim Climpy's Warfair Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Tim Climpy's Warfair is releasing on Early Access, 19th May 2023 (Was 5th May but not quite got through Steam review period yet :D) Wishlist now! (please)

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2050980/Tim_Climpys_Warfair/

Tim Climpy's Warfair is an Online FPS game by Common Blob featuring:
8 Maps
Multiple game modes
25 Weapons
200+ player customisations
Weapon customisation
Coming soon to Early Access!
